{"title":"七星石","authors":["阵容"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":7,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"七星石"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阵容"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斧凿的痕迹斑斑驳驳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"偏偏说是天上的七星陨落"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就这样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在心中凝固了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"神圣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成了抵足膜拜的枷锁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世世代代"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咀嚼着编造的传说"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竟然有滋有味地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"延续着香火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明眼人早已看穿了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可舌头被牵着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁也不敢把天机戳破"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可叹，愚昧压弯的腰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竟支不起自己的脑壳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一年三百六十日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就有三百六十个夜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不高高地扬起头来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞄一眼北斗七星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永恒的闪烁"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}